abstract: New York Jets cornerback Dexter McDougle, preparing with team for upcoming game against Miami Dolphins, lost valuable experience because of injuries, but has impressed coach Todd Bowles during workouts.
lead_paragraph: Dexter McDougle missed most of his senior season at Maryland and his rookie season with the Jets because of injuries, but he is making the most of his opportunities this season and has impressed his coaches.

headline.main: Jets Cornerback Puts His Scrappiness to Work
headline.print_headline: A Jet Delayed but Not Deterred
